		<img src="/figs/residence.png" alt="PDF preview" style="max-width: 70%; height: auto;" />
		<p style="text-align: left; font-size: 4rem; color: #555;"> 📑4. Qualitative comparison of Voyager against other baselines on the Rubble scene from MegaNeRF   </p>
		<img src="/figs/rubble.png" alt="PDF preview" style="max-width: 70%; height: auto;" />
